snippet.title: It Started With Hairs - Trailer
snippet.description:
Find the game itself here:
https://superbiasedgary.itch.io/it-started-with-hairs
Free on browser, PC, Mac, Linux and Android.

A 5-10 minute visual novel about the horror of having a body.
Content Warnings for descriptions of body horror and self harm.
